  "root_text": {
    "dhp320:0.1": "Khuddakanikāya ",
    "dhp320:0.2": "Dhammapada ",
    "dhp320:0.3": "Nāgavagga ",
    "dhp320:0.4": "Attadantavatthu ",
    "dhp320:1": "Ahaṁ nāgova saṅgāme, ",
    "dhp320:2": "cāpato patitaṁ saraṁ; ",
    "dhp320:3": "Ativākyaṁ titikkhissaṁ, ",
    "dhp320:4": "dussīlo hi bahujjano. ",
    "dhp321:1": "Dantaṁ nayanti samitiṁ, ",
    "dhp321:2": "dantaṁ rājābhirūhati; ",
    "dhp321:3": "Danto seṭṭho manussesu, ",
    "dhp321:4": "yotivākyaṁ titikkhati. ",
    "dhp322:1": "Varamassatarā dantā, ",
    "dhp322:2": "ājānīyā ca sindhavā; ",
    "dhp322:3": "Kuñjarā ca mahānāgā, ",
    "dhp322:4": "attadanto tato varaṁ. ",
    "dhp323:0": "Hatthācariyapubbakabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp323:1": "Na hi etehi yānehi, ",
    "dhp323:2": "gaccheyya agataṁ disaṁ; ",
    "dhp323:3": "Yathāttanā sudantena, ",
    "dhp323:4": "danto dantena gacchati. ",
    "dhp324:0": "Parijiṇṇabrāhmaṇaputtavatthu ",
    "dhp324:1": "Dhanapālo nāma kuñjaro, ",
    "dhp324:2": "Kaṭukabhedano dunnivārayo; ",
    "dhp324:3": "Baddho kabaḷaṁ na bhuñjati, ",
    "dhp324:4": "Sumarati nāgavanassa kuñjaro. ",
    "dhp325:0": "Pasenadikosalavatthu ",
    "dhp325:1": "Middhī yadā hoti mahagghaso ca, ",
    "dhp325:2": "Niddāyitā samparivattasāyī; ",
    "dhp325:3": "Mahāvarāhova nivāpapuṭṭho, ",
    "dhp325:4": "Punappunaṁ gabbhamupeti mando. ",
    "dhp326:0": "Sānusāmaṇeravatthu ",
    "dhp326:1": "Idaṁ pure cittamacāri cārikaṁ, ",
    "dhp326:2": "Yenicchakaṁ yatthakāmaṁ yathāsukhaṁ; ",
    "dhp326:3": "Tadajjahaṁ niggahessāmi yoniso, ",
    "dhp326:4": "Hatthippabhinnaṁ viya aṅkusaggaho. ",
    "dhp327:0": "Pāveyyakahatthivatthu ",
    "dhp327:1": "Appamādaratā hotha, ",
    "dhp327:2": "sacittamanurakkhatha; ",
    "dhp327:3": "Duggā uddharathattānaṁ, ",
    "dhp327:4": "paṅke sannova kuñjaro. ",
    "dhp328:0": "Sambahulabhikkhuvatthu ",
    "dhp328:1": "Sace labhetha nipakaṁ sahāyaṁ, ",
    "dhp328:2": "Saddhiṁ caraṁ sādhuvihāridhīraṁ; ",
    "dhp328:3": "Abhibhuyya sabbāni parissayāni, ",
    "dhp328:4": "Careyya tenattamano satīmā. ",
    "dhp329:1": "No ce labhetha nipakaṁ sahāyaṁ, ",
    "dhp329:2": "Saddhiṁ caraṁ sādhuvihāridhīraṁ; ",
    "dhp329:3": "Rājāva raṭṭhaṁ vijitaṁ pahāya, ",
    "dhp329:4": "Eko care mātaṅgaraññeva nāgo. ",
    "dhp330:1": "Ekassa caritaṁ seyyo, ",
    "dhp330:2": "Natthi bāle sahāyatā; ",
    "dhp330:3": "Eko care na ca pāpāni kayirā, ",
    "dhp330:4": "Appossukko mātaṅgaraññeva nāgo. ",
    "dhp331:0": "Māravatthu ",
    "dhp331:1": "Atthamhi jātamhi sukhā sahāyā, ",
    "dhp331:2": "Tuṭṭhī sukhā yā itarītarena; ",
    "dhp331:3": "Puññaṁ sukhaṁ jīvitasaṅkhayamhi, ",
    "dhp331:4": "Sabbassa dukkhassa sukhaṁ pahānaṁ. ",
    "dhp332:1": "Sukhā matteyyatā loke, ",
    "dhp332:2": "atho petteyyatā sukhā; ",
    "dhp332:3": "Sukhā sāmaññatā loke, ",
    "dhp332:4": "atho brahmaññatā sukhā. ",
    "dhp333:1": "Sukhaṁ yāva jarā sīlaṁ, ",
    "dhp333:2": "sukhā saddhā patiṭṭhitā; ",
    "dhp333:3": "Sukho paññāya paṭilābho, ",
    "dhp333:4": "pāpānaṁ akaraṇaṁ sukhaṁ. ",
    "dhp333:5": "Nāgavaggo tevīsatimo. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "dhp320:0.1": "Minor Collection ",
    "dhp320:0.2": "Sayings of the Dhamma 320–333 ",
    "dhp320:0.3": "23. Elephants ",
    "dhp320:1": "Like an elephant struck ",
    "dhp320:2": "with arrows in battle, ",
    "dhp320:3": "I shall endure abuse, ",
    "dhp320:4": "for so many folk are badly behaved. ",
    "dhp321:1": "The well-tamed beast is the one led to the crowd; ",
    "dhp321:2": "the tamed elephant’s the one the king mounts; ",
    "dhp321:3": "the tamed person who endures abuse ",
    "dhp321:4": "is the best of human beings. ",
    "dhp322:1": "Those who have tamed themselves are better ",
    "dhp322:2": "than fine tamed mules, ",
    "dhp322:3": "thoroughbreds from Sindh, ",
    "dhp322:4": "or giant tuskers. ",
    "dhp323:1": "For not on those mounts ",
    "dhp323:2": "would you go to the untrodden place, ",
    "dhp323:3": "whereas, with the help of one <j>whose self is well tamed, ",
    "dhp323:4": "you go there, tamed by the tamed. ",
    "dhp324:1": "The tusker named Dhanapāla ",
    "dhp324:2": "is musky in rut, hard to control. ",
    "dhp324:3": "Bound, he eats not a morsel, ",
    "dhp324:4": "for he misses the elephant forest. ",
    "dhp325:1": "One who gets drowsy from overeating, ",
    "dhp325:2": "fond of sleep, rolling round the bed ",
    "dhp325:3": "like a great hog stuffed with grain: ",
    "dhp325:4": "that dullard returns to the womb again and again. ",
    "dhp326:1": "In the past my mind wandered ",
    "dhp326:2": "how it wished, where it liked, as it pleased. ",
    "dhp326:3": "Now I’ll carefully guide it, ",
    "dhp326:4": "as a trainer with a hook guides a rutting elephant. ",
    "dhp327:1": "Delight in diligence! ",
    "dhp327:2": "Take good care of your mind! ",
    "dhp327:3": "Pull yourself out of this pit, ",
    "dhp327:4": "like an elephant sunk in a bog. ",
    "dhp328:1": "If you find an alert companion, ",
    "dhp328:2": "an attentive friend to live happily together, ",
    "dhp328:3": "then, overcoming all adversities, ",
    "dhp328:4": "wander with them, joyful and mindful. ",
    "dhp329:1": "If you find no alert companion, ",
    "dhp329:2": "no attentive friend to live happily together, ",
    "dhp329:3": "then, like a king who flees his conquered realm, ",
    "dhp329:4": "wander alone like a tusker in the wilds. ",
    "dhp330:1": "It’s better to wander alone, ",
    "dhp330:2": "there’s no fellowship with fools. ",
    "dhp330:3": "Wander alone and do no wrong, ",
    "dhp330:4": "at ease like a tusker in the wilds. ",
    "dhp331:1": "A friend in need is a blessing; ",
    "dhp331:2": "it’s a blessing to be content with whatever; ",
    "dhp331:3": "good deeds are a blessing at the end of life, ",
    "dhp331:4": "and giving up all suffering is a blessing. ",
    "dhp332:1": "In this world it’s a blessing to serve ",
    "dhp332:2": "one’s mother and one’s father. ",
    "dhp332:3": "And it’s a blessing also to serve ",
    "dhp332:4": "ascetics and brahmins. ",
    "dhp333:1": "It’s a blessing to keep precepts until you grow old; ",
    "dhp333:2": "a blessing to be grounded in faith; ",
    "dhp333:3": "the getting of wisdom’s a blessing; ",
    "dhp333:4": "and it’s a blessing to avoid doing wrong. "
  },
