    "dhp322:2": "ca → ājānīyāva (cck, sya1ed); ājānīyā vā (pts1ed) ",
    "dhp322:3": "Kuñjarā ca → kuñjarāva (cck, sya1ed); kuñjarā vā (pts1ed) ",
    "dhp324:1": "Dhanapālo → dhanapālako (bj, sya-all, km, pts1ed, pts2ed) ",
